r: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">事业</a>来。<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/shijian/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">时间</a>和<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/huanjing/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">环境</a>又不容许他们<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/jixu_25/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">继续</a><a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/yanjiu/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">研究</a>，不久他们<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/yuanyou_1/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">原有</a>的那一点<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/qianbo/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">浅薄</a><a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/xuewen/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">学问</a>也就逐渐荒疏，<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/zhongshen/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">终身</a>只在忙“糊口”。这样一来，他们的个人生就平<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/pingfan/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">平凡</a>凡地溜过去。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　大<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/bufen/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">部分</a>人<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/pingdan/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">平平淡淡</a>溜走的人生里，只有<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/pingdan/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">平淡</a>。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　现在的我听到的最多的一句话是“人生为何这样苦”和“人生为何这样的艰难”。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　可是，没有不<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/kunan/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">苦难</a>的人生。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/huiyi/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">回忆</a>里多半是<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/kuse/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">苦涩</a>掺杂着<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/tianmi/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">甜蜜</a>，以为苦涩所以擅自加上一点点甜，因为得不到的<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/yihan/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">遗憾</a>，它<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/zhuiyi/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">追忆</a>起来又是<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/yichang/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">异常</a>的苦。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　时间最最是<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/gongping/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">公平</a>，对于每个人来说。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1em; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\">　　<a href=\"http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/chuangtai/\" class=\"innerlink\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;\">窗台</a>上的那一份光，也走了。</p><p><br/></p>','2019-04-07 00:14:34','2f608a3346db4880abb09d3f219b665b','55edf69b31054633812a2bc0b4a6884e',36,0,0,0,0,0,'/upload/post/jsp/images/20190407/1554648553233085708.jpg');
